Hey! I took that same test today! Only I didn't study worth crap (I never 
study for tests) and spent almost the entire test time poking my friend 
through the space under the anti-copying board thingies. It was easy though. 
He finally got pissed of and threw his calculator at me.

Hope you did well, Firefox!

::Prowl::

Prowl runs back into the CR room, the gallon of liquid energon in his arms.

"Here ya go!" he says, stopping near Iron Raptor and thrusting the energon at 
her. "Anything else you need, love?"
